Title: apache_status: Fix wrong IPv6 URLs to query the information
Level: 1
Component: checks
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.4.0b4
Date: 1488546356

If the information from Apache is queried by IPv6, the request was denied,
because we created a bad request. Now IPv6 addresses are surrounded by
square bracket.
